title: #112 - Gus Johnson
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast we are joined by funny-man Gus "Danger" Johnson! Together we discuss delivering pizza to meth heads, the YouTube Haiku subreddit, anxiety attacks, preachers 'n sneakers, the pizza to cucumber quality scale, and Gus hits 1 million subscribers on his channel live during the show!!!
